Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.16,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,It's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:17.91,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.16,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:29.96,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Not only did you manage to avenge your sister,\N you even made it all the way here from the Far East.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:35.59,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Can I take your head as a prize for getting this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.81,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You have one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:48.15,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Descend two steps, and you may join me as an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:53.49,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,But if you would prefer death, ascend the remaining steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:57.74,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,When I first met you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:03.29,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...I was completely at the mercy of your malevolent charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:08.08,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,After that day, I was led down a path of utter failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.79,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,It was a fate worse than death!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:14.05,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I lived for nothing more than to do your bidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:19.10,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,But now, I've quelled my fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:21.64,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,All that's left is my will to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:26.48,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Even though two people in our group have died since our journey with Mr. Joestar first began...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.40,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...their deaths have only strengthened my resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:37.32,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,In that case, ascend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:44.87,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I see, I see, Polnareff...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.63,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,By descending the stairs, you have chosen to ally yourself with me, the mighty Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:00.35,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.64,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'm sure I just tried going up a step!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:07.64,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\N Have I weakened your unwavering resolve, Polnareff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:12.15,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Could it be that you truly do fear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:22.41,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Or did your subconscious fear \Ncause your body to act against your will?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.91,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,That's impossible! I'm sure I tried going up the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.92,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,W-What did he do?! Was it his Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:35.80,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.34,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,It was Dio's Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.64,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...The World?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.39,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,J-Just what can it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:26.16,Title 3,title,0,0,0,,{\fad(985,689)\pos(135,858)}Episode 45: Dio's World Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:26.99,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Polnareff, for what purpose do humans live?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:32.46,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,They live to attain peace of mind \Nby conquering their fears and anxieties.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.29,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Seeking fame...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.29,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...controlling others...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.51,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...and acquiring wealth are methods \Nby which they attain peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:45.43,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Some even choose to attain \Npeace of mind through friendships or marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:49.56,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,When humans express a willingness to help others,\N or proclaim their actions to be in the name of love or peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.77,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...their true motive is really to attain peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:56.81,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Attaining peace of mind is the true goal of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:02.19,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,So tell me, now that I have enlightened you,\N why do you still feel anxiety in serving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:06.03,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,This is the simplest path to attaining peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:12.04,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Doesn't the thought of challenging me, \Nknowing it may bring about your demise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.66,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,...give you anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:18.29,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,No way... Am I really subconsciously submitting to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.63,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You're a very powerful Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.30,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I would hate to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:27.84,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Will you sever your ties with Joestar and your friends, and come serve me for all of eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.56,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I promise it will bring you eternal peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.93,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'm at my limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.89,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Abdul, Iggy... give me courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.48,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Th-That's enough, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.07,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I already submitted to you once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:47.07,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I refuse to submit again before I've even seen your Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.87,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Then you leave me no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.46,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Prepare to meet your end, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.17,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Is that The World? Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:06.05,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Muda Muda Muda Muda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:06.05,Note,Note,0,0,0,,TN: Muda is a taunt/battle cry used to express futility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.27,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:22.77,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry anymore, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.32,Main,Jojobros,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dio!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.32,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Was that Dio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.66,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.03,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I need to tell you guys something first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:37.25,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I experienced The World's power just a moment ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:42.50,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,W-Well, I say experienced, but I didn't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.50,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I-I'll tell you exactly what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:51.80,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I thought I was climbing up the stairs toward him,\N but I kept going down instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.51,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I-I'm not sure I'm making any sense right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.81,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,...but I just can't explain what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.81,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,It felt like I was going insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:06.32,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,He wasn't using a simple trick like hypnosis or super speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.53,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,It was something strange and terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.29,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,What about Abdul and Iggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.42,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Th-They didn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.46,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,They died to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.05,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:42.27,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar, the sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.56,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,We need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.02,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.95,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Hey, Nimrod... What's above this floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.57,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,A-A tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.87,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,It's a single room at the very top!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.95,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,Lord Dio rests there during the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.20,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Is there any other way to the top?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.04,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,N-No... That's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.92,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,All right. Lead us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.43,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Ora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.31,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:32.65,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Even though I've never met him,\N I've known about this man for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.20,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,This has been a long time coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:40.12,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,I feel like I've known him since the day I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.95,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,So does Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.12,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,He brings back nothing but bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:51.21,Thoughts,Joseph,0,0,0,,The Joestar blood coursing through our veins has destined us to do battle with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.17,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:57.14,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Be it our journey thus far, or whatever will happen next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.97,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I regret none of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:05.39,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I've got a feeling in my gut,\N and it's telling me I'm on the side of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.40,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Dio is darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.27,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar and the others are on the side of light, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.74,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Even though I'm injured, my courage still grows stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:17.11,Thoughts,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'm on the side of light; the side of righteousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.74,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Attack as soon as the coffin opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.20,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,But be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.71,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,There's no telling if he's in there or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.25,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Nimrod, open it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:35.55,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,L-Lord Dio! I swear I haven't betrayed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:41.01,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,I only led them here because I believed you could defeat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:47.31,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,As surely as I believe pissing into the wind will wet your pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.61,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,Please understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.53,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth and open it up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:58.78,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,Please make sure these idiots die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.66,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,Lord Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.41,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.29,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:18.76,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,I-I'm inside the coffin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:22.18,Main,Nukesaku,0,0,0,,But I just opened the lid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.18,Secondary,Joseph,0,0,0,,W-What? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.60,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I had my eyes glued on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.23,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Did any of you see Nimrod go inside{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.19,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,No, get put inside the coffin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:35.44,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,N-No... I was watching him the entire time,\N but he appeared inside before I could tell what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:40.49,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Polnareff is right! This wasn't some kind of trick or super speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.87,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We're in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.91,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.96,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.50,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.34,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Polnareff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.17,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.85,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,What in the world was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:10.64,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I couldn't see a thing, but I felt something much more powerful than any Stand we've ever seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:15.23,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,It was like knowing a bulldozer is coming for you \Nby the sound of the engine alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:19.07,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I felt it, too! That cold, murderous intent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.99,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It felt like someone put an icicle up my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.99,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It would have taken us out one-by-one if we had tried to fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:43.43,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,This is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.64,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's almost sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:48.52,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,His time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:55.77,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Don't tell me we're gonna sit on our asses until sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.98,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'll make myself clear, Mr. Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.53,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm running away from this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:04.95,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I agree with Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:13.71,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,So do I, but the situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:19.25,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We've encountered his Stand, The World, yet we still have no idea what it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:26.14,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,If you climb a mountain without knowing which route you'll take,\N or where the summit is, you'll inevitably get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.51,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Inevitably!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:31.64,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,In fact, it's as inevitable as \Na good belch after drinking a refreshing cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.36,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Dio is definitely gonna come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:39.15,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He'll want to finish us off before sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:43.74,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We need to use this chance to discover his Stand's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.74,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's the only chance we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.74,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,No! I'm not running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.79,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Abdul and Iggy died for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:58.92,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'll use underhanded tactics,\N and burn in hell for it if I have to, but I refuse to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.80,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Wait, Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.26,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gramps, we can't stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.39,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Jotaro, tell us your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.72,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Polnareff will fight him in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.85,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,We'll fight him in retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.40,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.77,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...it's a pincer attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.15,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Hey, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.70,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I wanna buy your truck. Name your price.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:30.49,Main,Driver,0,0,0,,You kiddin' me?! I need it for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.66,Main,Driver,0,0,0,,What're you{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:36.83,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.27,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,There you are, Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:59.77,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Run away until sunrise? That ain't happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.77,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,I'll defeat you by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:08.03,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Even without knowing what your Stand is capable of,\N I have my ways of defeating you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.16,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,You're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.16,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Hold up, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:17.21,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Normally I'd leave a stubborn guy like you alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:20.88,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...but Gramps and Kakyoin wanted me to stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:21.96,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,...so here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.21,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.97,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,An automobile...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Such impressive power and speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.74,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,We only had horse-drawn carriages in my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.91,Main,Bodyguard,0,0,0,,Hey, pal! What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.13,Main,Bodyguard,0,0,0,,This is Senator Wilson Phillips' car!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.29,Main,Bodyguard,0,0,0,,Do I gotta make you spew blood from your eye sockets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:19.77,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,My, my... Young folks are so hot-blooded these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.57,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:27.44,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Silence yourself and get in the front seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:28.65,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,You will be driving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.20,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:34.91,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Do you think you can get away with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.12,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,No, of course he won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.12,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,Nobody can get away with doing this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.62,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I graduated from high school and college with top marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.13,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I was captain of the college wrestling team!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:49.72,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I became a politician since my peers admired and respected me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.80,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I own a one-thousand acre villa in Hawaii!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.80,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I married a gorgeous model twenty-five years my younger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.72,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I pay fifty times more in taxes than regular people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:01.64,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I've crushed every enemy on my path to become the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:05.40,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I'm Senator Wilson Phillips!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.07,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Listen up, whippersnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.48,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,I'll have you locked up for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.74,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Locked up for{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.16,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I won't repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.70,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.71,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the heck is this guy? He'll kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.25,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I'll die if I don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.88,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I'm dead meat if I can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.01,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Help... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.76,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.06,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:44.14,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,I just jumped outside, so h-how did I end up inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.81,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,How could this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.27,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Make haste until we reach the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.03,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,If you fail to reach it, I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.28,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,C-Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.57,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,How am I inside?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.74,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I know! It's because I'm a senator!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.45,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,There's nothing a senator can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:17.30,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I can feel his dark aura coming closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.97,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.81,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He's coming right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.60,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Can Dio tell exactly where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.36,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,No. Our shared connection is through the body of my grandfather, Jonathan Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.78,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We can sense each other \Nthrough an inexplicably shared wavelength...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:37.32,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,...but it's only good for knowing when the other is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:42.41,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,It's why I couldn't tell where the mansion was,\N even though we were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:47.87,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,The only thing he knows is that a Joestar is close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:51.04,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He can't tell the difference between Jotaro and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:55.55,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,I don't think he noticed that we split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.80,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.39,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,In the movies, the engine always starts right up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.90,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,W-We're stuck in traffic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.94,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Rush hour traffic at this time is bumper-to-bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:14.86,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.66,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,I would if I could, but I can't move an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.24,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The sidewalk is wide enough. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:23.24,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,The sidewalk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.37,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,It's packed with people heading home from work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.66,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,It matters not. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.92,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,C-Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.04,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Quickly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.71,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.85,Main,Jotaro,0,0,0,,It started. Hurry and get on, Polnareff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.27,Main,Polnareff,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.23,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,I've gone to great lengths for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:58.20,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,My life... You'll spare my life because I'm a senator, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.57,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,I will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:05.12,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,That's it! I'm dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:07.66,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,A senator like me could never die like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.83,Thoughts,Senator,0,0,0,,I'm dreaming! I'm dreaming! Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:15.46,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,There they are. Approach them. As close as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.59,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,The World is ineffective unless I am close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:22.89,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,He's getting closer! In that car! That's Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.85,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:30.98,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Kakyoin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.69,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Dio, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.36,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Emerald Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:52.87,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,W-What {\i1}is{\i0} he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:57.09,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,He didn't move from his seat,\N and he deflected my attack with one finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.92,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:07.68,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,He even deflected a concentrated splash! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.56,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,When did he call out his Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.98,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Impossible! How didn't I notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.49,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Just a bit too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:24.16,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,He flew out of The World's range.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.41,Main,Senator,0,0,0,,W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.54,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,What do I stand to gain from telling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:36.29,Main,Dio,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes forward and drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:44.97,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Be careful, Kakyoin! You got too close to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.55,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry... I-I couldn't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:56.35,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Several months ago, he said to me \N"There's no need to vomit with fright...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.48,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Be at peace. Be at peace, Kakyoin..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:03.57,Thoughts,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Dammit! Never again! I will never lose again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.61,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Kakyoin, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.82,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,Did you see The World?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:11.70,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Yeah... I attacked it from about ten meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:15.12,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Any closer, and he would have got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:20.46,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Now we know his Stand holds a secret \Nfar more frightening than anything we could have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.22,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,But I did discover two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:28.35,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,First, it can't travel a far distance \Nlike Hierophant Green or Hermit Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:33.56,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,It's short-ranged and powerful like Star Platinum, with an effective range of ten meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:38.36,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Second, it attacked with its fist,\N which means it probably doesn't use projectiles like bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:45.15,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,If we can get within ten meters of Dio undetected,\N I think we may stand a chance of defeating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.70,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We need to investigate carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:52.66,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,We can't be too cautious when dealing with an enemy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:56.79,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,That's strange... His car stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:03.09,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Watch out! Something's coming for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:08.76,Main,Joseph,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:09.72,Main,Kakyoin,0,0,0,,Mr. Joestar!
